Hampir kehilangan semua 
kejayaan kemenangan. 


463 
00:58:44,467 --> 00:58:45,675 
Hampir. 

464 
00:59:07,342 --> 00:59:09,425 
Halo Jenderal! Pria. 

465 
00:59:09,592 --> 00:59:12,342 
